Template for an email message sent to authorize a password reset.
Variables passed to this template:
    user: The SimpleUser\User instance.
    resetUrl: The link to click to reset the password.
#}

{# The subject line. #}
{%- block subject -%}{%- autoescape false -%}
Reset your password
{%- endautoescape -%}{%- endblock -%}

{# The plain text message. #}
{%- block body_text -%}{%- autoescape false -%}

Reset your password

Click the link below to reset your password:
{{ resetUrl }}


_______________________________________________________________
Didn't ask to reset your password?

If you didn't ask to reset your password, it's likely that
another user entered your username or email address by mistake
while trying to reset their password. If that's the case, you
don't need to take any further action and you can safely
disregard this email.

